transition from portrait to landscape (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30551\">#30551</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/d37b9b8e468b7b2c9cda8b27fe7019bb905ad2bf\">d37b9b8</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>segment-view:</strong> scroll to correct content when height is not set (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30547\">#30547</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/d14311fb65ae3de7ba7578791ce1ea44f186c413\">d14311f</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30543\">#30543</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
