    "body": "<h3>Bug Fixes</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>checkbox:</strong> ensure proper visual selection when navigating via VoiceOver in Safari (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30300\">#30300</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/bb40a1efe71237075db2f3a536eddeb1d7c400fc\">bb40a1e</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>overlays:</strong> exclude backdrop-no-scroll class when toast is presented (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30123\">#30123</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/7f9df7a89447e51eec0b1516069a1e0c9c9722e5\">7f9df7a</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30112\">#30112</a></li>\n<li><strong>segment-view:</strong> prevent vertical scroll while scrolling horizontally (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30276\">#30276</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/105796f6bc8f961f58ecbb101285097cc86891c0\">105796f</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30001\">#30001</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
