ng> trigger focus and blur on click (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30234\">#30234</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/ba8d8f489607537b3dac915cfc9f2c32a74b994c\">ba8d8f4</a>)</li>\n<li><strong>vue:</strong> update output target and properly emit events (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30227\">#30227</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/11554a5d3590c660dbf609931dcb63cc2daf79cb\">11554a5</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30206\">#30206</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30178\">#30178</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30177\">#30177</a> <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30170\">#30170</a></li>\n<li><strong>vue:</strong> update output target and resolve type issues (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30239\">#30239</a>) (<a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/commit/6dcb143307682793ac4fd46d03efa5868a49e87d\">6dcb143</a>), closes <a href=\"https://github.com/ionic-team/ionic-framework/issues/30179\">#30179</a></li>\n</ul>\n",
